title: O'Neill Gooru Comp Vest - SCOTT BYERLY
description: Our vests are developed and tested by the best athletes in the water. The O'Neill Gooru Comp Vest defies convention, sets a new industry standard, and leads the way for others to follow. Utilizing a unique pullover design, the zipperless, bucklefree, streamlined design will take you to new heights and unforseen performance levels.
